----------------
PST experiment for team LBI with high-speed camera. On the roof of the last bunker. Snow depth representative for this elevation. The layer of surface hoar is an oddity due to the close proximity of the creek, although we have found surcae hoar on shaded slopes at valley bottom throughout the Davos area.

PROFILE
-------
Only a few cm of new snow since yesterday. Some settlement of the slab, but overall still very soft.The layer below the thick crust was very variable (hardness 1 to 3) and consisted of many ice chunks mixed with facets.

RUTSCHBLOCK
-----------
no Rutschblock. 
2 PSTs: 22 PP and 32 PP

SNOW SURFACE
------------
About 60 cm foot penetration

SNOW DRIFT
----------
not much wind today

ALARM SIGNS
-----------
nothing observed but stayed mostly in our tracks from yesterday.

AVALANCHES
----------
no observations</slf:text></slf:profiletext></slf:profiletext-list></caaml:customData></caaml:metaData><caaml:timeRef><caaml:recordTime><caaml:TimeInstant><caaml:timePosition>2019-01-10T15:00:00+01:00</caaml:timePosition></caaml:TimeInstant></caaml:recordTime><caaml:dateTimeReport>2019-01-11T12:53:25+01:00</caaml:dateTimeReport><caaml:dateTimeLastEdit>2019-01-14T09:33:27+01:00</caaml:dateTimeLastEdit></caaml:timeRef><caaml:srcRef/><caaml:locRef><caaml:name>Davos - Fluelabach - SLF windtunnel</caaml:name><caaml:validElevation><caaml:ElevationPosition uom="m"><caaml:position>1640</caaml:position></caaml:ElevationPosition></caaml:validElevation><caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:SlopeAnglePosition uom="deg"><caaml:position>0</caaml:position></caaml:SlopeAnglePosition></caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:pointLocation><gml:Point id="pointID" srsName="urn:ogc:def:crs:OGC:1.3:CRS84" srsDimension="2"><gml:pos>9.869968 46.807735</gml:pos></gml:Point></caaml:pointLocation></caaml:locRef><caaml:snowProfileResultsOf><caaml:SnowProfileMeasurements dir="top down"><caaml:profileDepth uom="cm">88.0</caaml:profileDepth><caaml:weatherCond><caaml:airTempPres uom="degC">-7.3</caaml:airTempPres></caaml:weatherCond><caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:hS><caaml:Components><caaml:height uom="cm">88.0</caaml:height></caaml:Components></caaml:hS></caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:stratProfile><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">0.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">4.0</caaml:thickness><caaml:wetness uom="">D</caaml:wetness><caaml:grainFormPrimary>PP</caaml:grainFormPrimary><caaml:grainSize uom="mm"><caaml:Components><caaml:avg>0.5</caaml:avg><caaml:avgMax>1.0</caaml:avgMax></caaml:Components></caaml:grainSize><caaml:hardness uom="">F</caaml:hardness></caaml:Layer><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">4.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">9.0</caaml:thickness><caaml:wetness uom="">D</caaml:wetness><caaml:grainFormPrimary>DF</caaml:grainFormPrimary><caaml:grainSize uom="mm"><caaml:Components><caaml:a